Strong communities, we are not alone.
Other legit workshops.
Message EM-che to get access to other repos.

http://opensourceecology.org/wiki - Factor-e farm in Missouri. They repurpose metal scrap, especially in their designs. Open source.
http://sudoroom.org/wiki - Hackerspace in Oakland. You can join the mailing list of hackers as well. They have a tool shop there including drill, saws, press saw, dremel, pliers, hammers, screws, nails, grinder well equipped.
http://hackerspaces.org/ - Designs to the hackerspaces. Over.
https://groups.google.com/d/forum/soil-age - Soil age. Victory.
https://groups.google.com/forum/?hl=en#!forum/food_crisis - Looters? Food Crisis forum with largest US food advocates and organizations.

Other legit tool shops and groups of people? Upload ~ push ~ EC. <3 Anonymous.

